Package: debian-btrfs-iso-udeb
Version: 0.1
Section: debian-installer
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Package-Type: udeb
Depends: partman-base, btrfs-progs-udeb
Maintainer: Debian BTRFS ISO Maintainers <maintainer@example.invalid>
Description: Btrfs subvolume setup hook for Debian Installer
 This installer component adds a partman finish hook that converts the
 installed Btrfs root into the project's subvolume layout and copies the
 post-install Snapper helper scripts into the target system.
